#!/bin/bash
# Daily backup of small VPS state not covered by Ansible/git:
# Guacamole connections, Traefik certs (acme.json), Pi-hole config,
# OpenClaw agent runtime (memory/workspaces, secrets excluded), agent dashboard
# state + secrets.
# Deployed by ansible (vps_backup role).
set -euo pipefail

BACKUP_ROOT="{{ vps_backup_root }}"
RETENTION_DAYS={{ vps_backup_retention_days }}
STAMP=$(date +%F_%H%M)

backup_tar() {
  local name="$1" src="$2"; shift 2
  local dir="$BACKUP_ROOT/$name"
  mkdir -p "$dir" && chmod 700 "$dir"
  tar -czf "$dir/${name}_${STAMP}.tar.gz" -C "$src" "$@" .
  find "$dir" -name "${name}_*.tar.gz" -mtime +$RETENTION_DAYS -delete
}

# Guacamole: connection config + embedded DB (docker volume)
backup_tar guacamole /var/lib/docker/volumes/guacamole_guacamole_config/_data

# Traefik: acme.json (LE certs) + static/dynamic config
backup_tar traefik /srv/docker/oracle-cloud/traefik

# Pi-hole: config only — query history and gravity DBs are regenerable
backup_tar pihole /srv/docker/oracle-cloud/etc-pihole \
  --exclude='./pihole-FTL.db*' --exclude='./gravity*.db' \
  --exclude='./listsCache' --exclude='./gravity_backups' --exclude='./config_backups'
backup_tar pihole-dnsmasq /srv/docker/oracle-cloud/etc-dnsmasq.d

# OpenClaw: agent memory/workspaces/config — secrets (.env) and logs excluded
backup_tar openclaw /home/openclaw/.openclaw \
  --exclude='./.env' --exclude='*.env' --exclude='./logs'

# Agent dashboard: shared memory, history, proposals + .env (Telegram/Garage/Apple secrets)
backup_tar dashboard /srv/dashboard --exclude='./node_modules'
